            <p><lb n="1"/><g type="ddanda"/> svasti śa<add place="above">ka</add>-varṣătīta <num value="786">78<unclear>6</unclear></num>
                <lb n="2"/>Āṣāḍha-māsa pañcamĭ kr̥ṣṇa-pa<lb 
